26#include <sys/cdefs.h>
27__KERNEL_RCSID(0, "$NetBSD: nouveau_nvkm_engine_disp_nv04.c,v 1.2 2018/08/27 04:58:31 riastradh Exp $");
28
29#include "priv.h"
30
31static const struct nvkm_disp_oclass *
32nv04_disp_root(struct nvkm_disp *disp)
33{
34 return &nv04_disp_root_oclass;
35}
36
37static void
38nv04_disp_vblank_init(struct nvkm_disp *disp, int head)
39{
40 struct nvkm_device *device = disp->engine.subdev.device;
41 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x600140 + (head * 0x2000) , 0x00000001);
42}
43
44static void
45nv04_disp_vblank_fini(struct nvkm_disp *disp, int head)
46{
47 struct nvkm_device *device = disp->engine.subdev.device;
48 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x600140 + (head * 0x2000) , 0x00000000);
49}
50
51static void
52nv04_disp_intr(struct nvkm_disp *disp)
53{
54 struct nvkm_subdev *subdev = &disp->engine.subdev;
55 struct nvkm_device *device = subdev->device;
56 u32 crtc0 = nvkm_rd32(device, 0x600100);
57 u32 crtc1 = nvkm_rd32(device, 0x602100);
58 u32 pvideo;
59
60 if (crtc0 & 0x00000001) {
61 nvkm_disp_vblank(disp, 0);
62 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x600100, 0x00000001);
63 }
64
65 if (crtc1 & 0x00000001) {
66 nvkm_disp_vblank(disp, 1);
67 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x602100, 0x00000001);
68 }
69
70 if (device->chipset >= 0x10 && device->chipset <= 0x40) {
71 pvideo = nvkm_rd32(device, 0x8100);
72 if (pvideo & ~0x11)
73 nvkm_info(subdev, "PVIDEO intr: %08x\n", pvideo);
74 nvkm_wr32(device, 0x8100, pvideo);
75 }
76}
77
78static const struct nvkm_disp_func
79nv04_disp = {
80 .intr = nv04_disp_intr,
81 .root = nv04_disp_root,
82 .head.vblank_init = nv04_disp_vblank_init,
83 .head.vblank_fini = nv04_disp_vblank_fini,
84};
85
86int
87nv04_disp_new(struct nvkm_device *device, int index, struct nvkm_disp **pdisp)
88{
89 return nvkm_disp_new_(&nv04_disp, device, index, 2, pdisp);
90}
